The Hash Slinging Snacker BOT 07/19/2023 11:39 PM
Hi, welcome to your confessional channel! This is a place for you to dump all of your thoughts about the game, just like confessionals on the actual show! Throughout the game, you will also receive questions about things going on in the game in this channel. These can either be from a member of production, or from a spectator. (If it is a question from a spectator, it will need to be pre-approved by production before you can see it.) We encourage you to share as many of your thoughts on anything and anyone in the game as you’re comfortable with! This is a place for people to see a log of your journey from day 1 to final tribal council. Right now, the only people who have access to viewing your confessionals are members of Production, and our Super Spectators! Super Spectators are all vetted & trusted individuals in the community, so you don’t have to worry about any leaks. If you want to make sure ONLY members of production can see a message, you should use your submissions channel instead. That channel will also be used for challenge submissions. Congrats once again on being casted! For now, feel free to give the specs a quick intro! Where are you from, how old are you, what are you into?
